{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that there's anything wrong with being any of those kinds of things, but that's what I-- Uncle Rudi was exactly the opposite.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a sportsman and a practical man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he loved cars, for example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we-- I actually have the receipts here-- the number of cars that he bought for 5 pounds and 3 pounds and sold for 10 pounds kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In particular, I remember when we were there in 1936-- and we have a photograph here-- is of a Bullnose Morris Cowley that we had with a dickey seat at the back thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we toured around-- he, he, he drove us around London in that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were very few cars in those days, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and it was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he showed as all his photographs of when he played football in goal for the Nuremberg University, where he'd studied.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was a great swimmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he showed us photographs of him doing swallow dives from the highest Olympic boards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all of those sorts of things he was really interested in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And England suited him to the grand because of the-- sports, you know, was always the overriding importance kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the papers was always about sports, football and cricket and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he loved it until his dying days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He used to watch every weekend and Jimmy Hill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He used to ring up Jimmy Hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he used to talk about the match with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was the sort of person that I wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, and maybe he had a big influence on me in those days in 1936.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One of the particular things I remember in those days, in London, was the trolley buses.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
